summary: This document is a Certificate of Existence issued by Osbert E. Potter, the Lieutenant Governor of the Virgin Islands, certifying that Prytanee, LLC is duly organized under the laws of the United States Virgin Islands. It confirms the company's perpetual duration and that it has paid all applicable fees.

persons.name: Osbert E. Potter
persons.context: Osbert E. Potter is the issuing authority of the Certificate of Existence for Prytanee, LLC.

keyFacts: Prytanee, LLC filed Articles of Organization on July 22, 2016.
The company is organized under the laws of the United States Virgin Islands.
The duration of Prytanee, LLC is perpetual.
All applicable fees have been paid by the company.
No Articles of Termination have been filed by the company.
